egypt about 54000 egyptians working in iraq and kuwait have 
returned home at least 12 million egyptians were working in the 
two countries before the crisis began and they contributed a large 
chunk of the 35 billion of foreign remittances every year trade 
with iraq which stood at 74 million last year is frozen 
</TEXT>
