lebanon fuel prices have quadrupled and food prices have 
doubled since iraqs invasion the lebanese pound has plummeted to 
an alltime low of 850 to the dollar kuwait was at the forefront 
of a 2 billion reconstruction plan in lebanon which has been 
devastated by 15 years of civil war 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
pakistan remittances from 180000 pakistanis in iraq and 
kuwait have dried up 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
philippines devastated by an earthquake last month the 
philippines faces the return of 93000 of its citizens working in 
iraq and kuwait the two countries also supplied 225 percent of 
the philippines fuel needs 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
romania iraq owes romania 17 billion in export credit 
</TEXT>
