unified defense strategy to complement the usled military 
buildup in saudi arabia 
abdullah bishara the general secretary of the gulf alliance 
told kuwaiti television before the meeting that the council has 
decided to muster the troops of the penisula shield rapid 
deployment force the force of up to 10000 troops from six gulf 
nations has been based for the last two years at the northeastern 
saudi base of hafr albaten 
arab league foreign ministers were to meet in emergency session 
on monday but an egyptian foreign ministry official said the 
gathering had been rescheduled for aug 30 he did not say how many 
nations had agreed to attend 
baghdad has expressed willingness to negotiate with the united 
states but white house spokesman marlin fitzwater dismissed the 
offer tuesday as the same old litany from iraq he said no 
talks are possible until iraq withdraws its tens of thousands of 
troops from kuwait 
in a speech directed at bush saddam defended detaining 
foreigners and promised a major catastrophe if fighting breaks 
out 
of the 3000 americans trapped in iraq and kuwait by the 
invasion 54 are believed to have been seized by iraqi authorities 
the state department said tuesday iraq says it is using some as 
human shields at military installations 
the british foreign office said today that 21 britons are known 
to be held at iraqi military installations british foreign 
secretary douglas hurd denounced saddam today as a destructive 
loser whose hostagetaking reflects his isolation in the region 
and the world 
iraqs reported willingness to release european community 
citizens from kuwait could be an attempt to split the western 
