said canal officials 
the saratoga joins the carriers eisenhower in the red sea and 
the independence stationed in the arabian sea just outside the 
persian gulf a fourth aircraft carrier the kennedy is enroute to 
the mediterranean 
more than 25 us warships are in the region britain france 
and the soviet union also have warships in the area belgium and 
australia have vessels on the way 
french military sources said today a reconnaissance squadron 
the first french ground forces being sent to the area would likely 
leave today for the united arab emirates 
