the turbine generator prompted an automatic shutdown said plant 
spokesman ron sher 
seabrook began supplying enough electricity for 1 million homes 
sunday after a fivemonth testing program 
all seven shutdowns since the reactor was connected to the new 
england power grid were turbinerelated and the plant was shut down 
for about a month in april for turbine modifications 
todays shutdown occurred during scheduled maintenance 
activities that were taking place on a turbine control system not 
the turbine itself sher said 
seabrook opponents see the shutdowns as confirmation of their 
longheld predictions 
weve been talking about construction problems bad quality 
control for years said sam miller of the clamshell alliance 
the plant took 10 years to complete 19761986 and its 
operating license was delayed until last spring by people 
protesting emergency evacuation plans near the plant 
