wedge at the top of the gulf of aqaba between jordanian and 
egyptian land egypt rejected the offer 
the congestion at aqaba is duplicated on a smaller scale in some 
parts of the capital hotels in amman are full the airport is 
jammed and the embassies of most asian and african countries are 
besieged 
the minister of religious affairs ali faqir ordered all 
